M|references|Real-world examples of successful referral programs.
M|references|- Dropbox (Classic)
M|references|- Uber/Lyft
M|references|- Morning Brew
M|references|- Notion
M|references|- Incentive Types Comparison
M|references|- Incentive Sizing Framework
M|references|- Viral Coefficient & Metrics (Key Metrics, Calculating Referral Program ROI)
M|references|**Program:** Give 500MB storage, get 500MB storage
M|references|**Why it worked:**
M|references|- Reward directly tied to product value
M|references|- Low friction (just an email)
M|references|- Both parties benefit equally
M|references|- Gamified with progress tracking
M|references|**Program:** Give $10 ride credit, get $10 when they ride
M|references|**Why it worked:**
M|references|- Immediate, clear value
M|references|- Double-sided incentive
M|references|- Easy to share (code/link)
M|references|- Triggered at natural moments
M|references|**Program:** Tiered rewards for subscriber referrals
M|references|- 3 referrals: nl stickers
M|references|- 5 referrals: T-shirt
M|references|- 10 referrals: Mug
M|references|- 25 referrals: Hoodie
M|references|**Why it worked:**
M|references|- Gamification drives ongoing engagement
M|references|- Physical rewards are shareable (more referrals)
M|references|- Low cost relative to subscriber value
M|references|- Built status/identity
M|references|**Program:** $10 credit per referral (education)
M|references|**Why it worked:**
M|references|- Targeted high-sharing audience (students)
M|references|- Product naturally spreads in teams
M|references|- Credit keeps users engaged
M|references|| Type | Pros | Cons | Best For |
M|references||------|------|------|----------|
M|references|| Cash/credit | Universally valued | Feels transactional | Marketplaces, fintech |
M|references|| Product credit | Drives usage | Only valuable if they'll use it | SaaS, subscriptions |
M|references|| Free months | Clear value | May attract freebie-seekers | Subscription products |
M|references|| Feature unlock | Low cost to you | Only works for gated features | Freemium products |
M|references|| Swag/gifts | Memorable, shareable | Logistics complexity | Brand-focused companies |
M|references|| Charity donation | Feel-good | Lower personal motivation | Mission-driven brands |
M|references|**Calculate your maximum incentive:**
M|references|```
M|references|Max Referral Reward = (Customer LTV × Gross Margin) - Target CAC
M|references|```
M|references|**Example:**
M|references|- LTV: $1,200
M|references|- Gross margin: 70%
M|references|- Target CAC: $200
M|references|- Max reward: ($1,200 × 0.70) - $200 = $640
M|references|**Typical referral rewards:**
M|references|- B2C: $10-50 or 10-25% of first purchase
M|references|- B2B SaaS: $50-500 or 1-3 months free
M|references|- Enterprise: Higher, often custom
M|references|**Viral coefficient (K-factor):**
M|references|```
M|references|K = Invitations × Conversion Rate
M|references|K > 1 = Viral growth (each user brings more than 1 new user)
M|references|K < 1 = Amplified growth (referrals supplement other acquisition)
M|references|```
M|references|**Example:**
M|references|- Average customer sends 3 invitations
M|references|- 15% of invitations convert
M|references|- K = 3 × 0.15 = 0.45
M|references|**Referral rate:**
M|references|```
M|references|Referral Rate = (Customers who refer) / (Total customers)
M|references|```
M|references|Benchmarks:
M|references|- Good: 10-25% of customers refer
M|references|- Great: 25-50%
M|references|- Exceptional: 50%+
M|references|**Referrals per referrer:**
M|references|Benchmarks:
M|references|- Average: 1-2 referrals per referrer
M|references|- Good: 2-5
M|references|- Exceptional: 5+
M|references|```
M|references|Referral Program ROI = (Revenue from referred customers - Program costs) / Program costs
M|references|Program costs = Rewards paid + Tool costs + Management time
M|references|```
M|references|**Track separately:**
M|references|- Cost per referred customer (CAC via referral)
M|references|- LTV of referred customers (often higher than average)
M|references|- Payback period for referral rewards